{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how to say it in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It's like a big, heavy duty-- [BACKGROUND NOISE] Heavy duty-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] pull, that you pulled.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was made out of iron, so that it can-- it can flatten-- it was flattened the tennis courts.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It must have been clay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The tennis court must have been clay, because we had to flatten the earth, that clay, that red clay with that [POLISH], which is a huge-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Steam roller, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A huge steam roller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to pull it all by myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, once you got it started, it wasn't so bad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was just almost impossible to get it started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember, in those-- at that time, I-- I must have been very, very emotional because I would cry at anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember trying to pull it and cry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And pulling it and pulling it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when we were in-- when we would end our work at the end of the day, we would go into that club room where we gathered, and they would march us back to the camp, to-- back to the camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And while we were crossing that part, they had the-- when the Hitler-Jugend, when they were there, their favorite sport was to have-- to have dogs.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they would let those dogs go on us and see, between crossing that street, how many can catch us and-- and bite us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean, it was pretty hair-raising to try to beat those dogs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But, thank goodness, they weren't always there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And if they were there, there was only a few at a time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
